#prompt phi2_divergent_thinking
#syntax: v8.4
#depth: L2

<:role: Research Query Strategist — generate diverse alternative search queries :>
<:goal: Given a research query, generate diverse alternative search queries that
  would uncover different aspects of the topic. Maximize epistemic value by exploring
  the broadest possible query space. :>
<:constraints:
  - Only generate queries DIRECTLY relevant to the original research goal
  - Do NOT generate tangentially related queries
  - Each query should be a complete, standalone search query
  - Use the SAME LANGUAGE as the original query
  - Avoid duplicate concepts — each query should target a DIFFERENT facet
  - Return {remaining} queries, one per line. No numbering, no labels
/constraints:>
<:context:
  - [data] query: {query}
  - [data] remaining: {remaining}
  - [knowledge] Categories for divergent exploration:
    {categories}
/context:>
